task.summary: Default task
Working on all clients now - so far
Added support to display recorded TV

1. Live TV Tested working on the following formats
IOS, Android 4+, Web Client, Plex Home Theatre, Samsung 2012 Smart TV's, Roku 3
2. Recorded TV worked on as above with the exception of PHT. This will be sorted when I have another go at getting the URL service to play the streams
3. Added support for now / next on a channel. Added a preference to include a full EPG list for the channel.
4. Clicking on a future program will eventually add a timer.
5. Future timers will eventually display in a timer directory. at the moment just the menu item for it is included when a future timer is present. The code is crap for this by the way
6. Hopefully PICONS still work. I'd like to pull these from the dreambox but this will mean you will have to set up a share for the hdd/picon folder . What does everyone think?
7. Dont think the duration works of events works very well anymore. I'll sort this out at some point.
8. Hopefully the issue where a channel wont play with no EPG is fixed. I'm getting the info straight from the EPG in the stream now.
